        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 50. Labels. i Drymaeus punctatus da Costa, 1907 ii Bulinus pupiformis Broderip in Broderip and Sowerby I 1832 iii Bulimus purpuratus Reeve, 1849 iv Bulinus pustulosus Broderip in Broderip and Sowerby I 1832 v Bulimus (Otostomus) quadrifasciatus Angas, 1878 vi Bulimus quitensis Pfeiffer, 1848." , "Figure 46. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) punctatus da Costa, 1907, lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.20 (H = 36.6) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) pulcherrimus (H. Adams, 1867), holotype NHMUK 1867.5.18.3 (H = 39.1) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) subhybridus (da Costa, 1906), holotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.127 (H = 49.1) J-L Drymaeus (Drymaeus) geometricus (Pfeiffer, 1846), lectotype NHMUK 1975564 (H = 34.6). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26817" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26718" .

